Developer Terms of Use
des:
Caren™, The Voice of Care, is GoMo Health’s go-to resource for the patient who needs in the moment answers to commonly asked questions related to healthcare, treatments, medications, tests and other condition specific information. Caren is easy to use – activate her with your voice request and she’ll immediately respond to you – just like an in-person conversation!

This tool is for informational and educational purposes only, and is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. Always call your doctor for your clinical care. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number. This skill does not collect personal information or provide access to personalized health information.

About GoMo Health

GoMo Health® is a leader in population health management and patient engagement solutions that support the continuum of care, and improved patient satisfaction. GoMo Health Concierge Care® personalizes patient interactions using our proprietary science, Behavioral Rx™, The Science of Population Health, building trust and credibility to motivate higher levels of reciprocity and actions. In partnership with health care organizations worldwide, GoMo Health® delivers a highly scalable and cost-effective solution for the management of high-risk, chronic, and complex conditions, enabling better self-management, healthy decision making, and improved outcomes. www.gomohealth.com
